Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.72,0:21:22.19,ED Rom,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.01\1a&HFE&\3a&HFE&\blur15\fad(200,200)}Eu me tornei sua capa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:32.86,ED Rom,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.01\1a&HFE&\3a&HFE&\blur15\fad(200,200)}Toque-me com suas mãos, seus dedos
