Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.88,0:21:56.35,ED Rom,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.01\1a&HFE&\3a&HFE&\blur15\fad(200,200)}Você me mostrou a sua mão
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.35,0:21:59.49,ED Rom,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.01\1a&HFE&\3a&HFE&\blur15\fad(200,200)}Toque-me mais fundo
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.59,0:20:41.19,ED Rom,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.01\1a&HFE&\3a&HFE&\blur4\fad(200,200)}No mundo cheio de coisas desconhecidas
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.46,0:20:46.73,ED Rom,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.01\1a&HFE&\3a&HFE&\blur4\fad(200,200)}monooto hitotsu ni mo obieru no ni
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.35,0:20:52.90,ED Rom,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.01\1a&HFE&\3a&HFE&\blur4\fad(200,200)}kono me o fusaindemo, mabuta no ura ni
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.90,0:20:56.66,ED Rom,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.01\1a&HFE&\3a&HFE&\blur4\fad(200,200)}ukande shimau hodo no kimi da
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.56,0:21:03.81,ED Rom,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.01\1a&HFE&\3a&HFE&\blur4\fad(200,200)}kazoe kirenai hodo no kirikizu ga tsuite
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.25,0:21:10.03,ED Rom,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.01\1a&HFE&\3a&HFE&\blur4\fad(200,200)}toumei janaku natta garasu mitai na boku no
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.03,0:21:15.72,ED Rom,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.01\1a&HFE&\3a&HFE&\blur4\fad(200,200)}hetakuso na egao sae ukeirete kureta
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.72,0:21:22.19,ED Rom,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.01\1a&HFE&\3a&HFE&\blur4\fad(200,200)}kimi no kasa ni narou
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.90,0:21:32.86,ED Rom,,0,0,0,,{\shad0.01\1a&HFE&\3a&HFE&\blur4\fad(200,200)}sono te de, sono yubi de, furete
